def-en: In the context of negative sampling, the process of creating a negative sample by replacing the object $o$ in a triple $(s,p,o)$ with another node.
def-ga: I gcomhthéacs frith-shamplála, an próiseas a bhaineann le frith-shampla a chruthú tríd an gcuspóir $c$ in abairt thriarach $(a,f,c)$ a ionadú le nód eile.
